<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">乘数尾5法，是指乘数尾数为5，被乘数为偶数时，可先将被乘数缩小2倍，同时将乘数扩大2倍，然后相乘，即为所求的积，可利用公式</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">a×b=(a÷2)×(b×2)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算，其中a、b表示被乘数与乘数。</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">36×25=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 36×25</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=(36÷2)×(25×2)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=18×50</Run>
    </Paragraph>  
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=900</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>